tateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"hero-main-cta\"><a href=\"https://docs.bitcoincomputer.io/start/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button button-blue w-inline-block\"><div class=\"button-flex-container\"><div>See our quickstart guide</div></div></a></div></div></div></section><section data-w-id=\"7a401da5-208d-1e5d-47b8-653cf303e9e1\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-customers\"><div class=\"bento-text\"><div data-w-id=\"12ad5871-2bc0-a28f-bf75-bf915f1cad39\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">Works on</div></div></div><div class=\"wrapper relative hidden\"><div class=\"customers-list\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759ec98275159de1c9600f_bitcoin-btc-logo.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-2\"/><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759e41cd2829350732fcb0_litecoin-ltc-logo.png\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759e41cd2829350732fcb0_litecoin-ltc-logo-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759e41cd2829350732fcb0_litecoin-ltc-logo-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759e41cd2829350732fcb0_litecoin-ltc-logo-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759e41cd2829350732fcb0_litecoin-ltc-logo-p-1600.png 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67759e41cd2829350732fcb0_litecoin-ltc-logo.png 2000w\" alt=\"\" class=\"image\"/><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/6796ac39b84ddfdd81b1fdcf_dogecoin-doge-logo-alternative.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-4\"/><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/6796ac0858e0430e762972ed_P_iconOnly_onWhite_RGB%20[Converted].svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-3\"/><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67ae4ab12ad8d268f53530b3_a21f8ceaa040c684b975bb49c3a1cbf3_bch.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-5\"/></div></div></section><div class=\"bento-text\"><div data-w-id=\"4c000f2f-636f-26a6-bf5d-fcd17c55e481\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">benefits</div></div><h2 data-w-id=\"4c000f2f-636f-26a6-bf5d-fcd17c55e484\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"bento-text-headline\"><strong class=\"bold-text\">Goodbye solidity, Hello Javascript</strong></h2><h5 data-w-id=\"4c000f2f-636f-26a6-bf5d-fcd17c55e487\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"bento-text-description\"><strong class=\"bold-text\">Write smart contracts in a language you know and love</strong></h5></div><section class=\"section-bento\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"bento-grid\"><div class=\"bento-row col-2\"><div id=\"w-node-_14f4b41e-8ae5-f89c-bbd9-0b512f0c8d86-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"14f4b41e-8ae5-f89c-bbd9-0b512f0c8d86\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el\"><div class=\"bento-el-text\"><h5>Use Your Favorite Tools</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Your favorite IDE, existing package managers, and well established linters and testing environments aren&#x27;t just familiar, they&#x27;re also secure and robust. You can now use them to develop decentralized applications.<br/></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el-img-container\"><div class=\"blocks-el-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67a14e05f9324900b5f8820b_0ac221581d5165eed8a5d52bf2470104_js-tools.png\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"391.5\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-el-img\"/></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_14f4b41e-8ae5-f89c-bbd9-0b512f0c8d7d-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"14f4b41e-8ae5-f89c-bbd9-0b512f0c8d7d\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el wide\"><div class=\"bento-el-text\"><h5>Run Smart Contracts in the Browser and in Node.js</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Modern Javascript engines are optimized for high performance and security by the worlds premier tech companies. You can now leverage this performance to execute smart contracts.<br/></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67a14e05cb074e15627eab45_b787f407a05b106783dab90387df6dd0_browser-icons.png\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"391.5\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-el-img\"/></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"bento-text\"><div data-w-id=\"7ac58af2-d289-2946-2db5-38f704d3b129\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">ADvantages</div></div><h2 data-w-id=\"7ac58af2-d289-2946-2db5-38f704d3b12c\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"bento-text-headline\"><strong class=\"bold-text\">Pure Bitcoin</strong></h2><h5 data-w-id=\"7ac58af2-d289-2946-2db5-38f704d3b12f\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"bento-text-description\"><strong class=\"bold-text\">Build never seen before applications</strong></h5></div><section class=\"section-bento\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"bento-grid\"><div class=\"bento-row col-2\"><div id=\"w-node-_644e84a2-abbc-d694-c21f-7dfc5b3e22d4-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"644e84a2-abbc-d694-c21f-7dfc5b3e22d4\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el\"><div class=\"bento-el-text\"><h5>Low Fixed Fees</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">The cost of evaluating smart contracts is independent of the number of computational steps on Bitcoin Computer. This is because only the users that are interested in a smart contract will execute it&#x27;s code - as opposed to over 1M validators with Ethereum.<br/></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67a64bc8f1a2f375c0c1ee5e_low-fixed-fees.png\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-el-img\"/></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_644e84a2-abbc-d694-c21f-7dfc5b3e22c9-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"644e84a2-abbc-d694-c21f-7dfc5b3e22c9\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el\"><div class=\"bento-el-text\"><h5>Trustless &amp; Decentralized</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Bitcoin Computer runs directly on Bitcoin and Bitcoin-like blockchains. That means no trusted third party or custodian between your application and the blockchain. <br/><br/>Bitcoin Computer enables self-custody and nobody can turn it off or prevent you from using it. </div></div><div class=\"blocks-el-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67a64b9453ca36b00b7f3f79_449ecff43f4a075db945cb7f080e6088_pure-bitcoin.png\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-el-img\"/></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"bento-text\"><div data-w-id=\"a571851e-bc09-1197-d269-6312b1e9dd35\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">Features</div></div><h5 class=\"heading-3\">Security, Simplicity &amp; Privacy</h5></div><section class=\"section-bento\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"bento-grid\"><div class=\"bento-row col-2\"><div id=\"w-node-_40617705-6301-ef4d-f91b-e8161910711e-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"40617705-6301-ef4d-f91b-e8161910711e\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el v2\"><div class=\"bento-el-text v2\"><h5>Miner Enforced Data Ownership</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Updating someone else&#x27;s smart contract data is as hard as stealing someone else&#x27;s Bitcoin.</div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_40617705-6301-ef4d-f91b-e81619107126-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"40617705-6301-ef4d-f91b-e81619107126\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el v2\"><div class=\"bento-el-text v2\"><h5>Built-In Encryption </h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Easy-to-use encryption helps you guarantee your users&#x27; privacy.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bento-row col-2\"><div id=\"w-node-_70904f5d-3c0a-07a7-c995-8deb4447acc9-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"70904f5d-3c0a-07a7-c995-8deb4447acc9\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el v2\"><div class=\"bento-el-text v2\"><h5>On and Off-Chain Data Storage</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Flexible data storage supports gaming, DeFi, and digital asset applications.</div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-f04475e1-d657-b3cc-e765-883d30520bdb-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"f04475e1-d657-b3cc-e765-883d30520bdb\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el v2\"><div class=\"bento-el-text v2\"><h5>Historical States</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">All previous states are preserved. All updates are timestamped and cryptographically signed.</div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_2dbc6536-4456-b85f-d75a-da7ddcaf6b93-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"2dbc6536-4456-b85f-d75a-da7ddcaf6b93\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"bento-el v2\"><div class=\"bento-el-text v2\"><h5>GDPR, CCPA &amp; AML Ready</h5><div class=\"bento-el-description\">Built from the ground up to make compliance with privacy laws easy.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wrapper\"></div></section><div class=\"icons-sticky-container\"><div id=\"w-node-_105ceefc-d6a6-25bb-557d-a488a381a398-c62a963d\" class=\"icons-sticky-headline\"><div data-w-id=\"105ceefc-d6a6-25bb-557d-a488a381a399\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name black\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">Things You Can Build</div></div><h3 data-w-id=\"105ceefc-d6a6-25bb-557d-a488a381a39c\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\">Bringing the Most Popular Web3 Apps To Bitcoin </h3></div><div id=\"w-node-_105ceefc-d6a6-25bb-557d-a488a381a39e-c62a963d\" class=\"icons-sticky-list\"><div class=\"icons-sticky-el\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/674cf6e365dc4707c62a9962_icons-sticky-icon-1.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"icons-sticky-el-img\"/><div class=\"icons-sticky-el-text\"><h5>Games</h5><p class=\"text-p-faded-2\">Create and monetize everything without taking custody of player funds.<br/><br/>Monetize user-to-user payments, tournaments, and new game elements like campaigns, levels, maps, items, or achievements.</p></div></div><div class=\"icons-sticky-el\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/674cf6e365dc4707c62a9961_icons-sticky-icon-3.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"icons-sticky-el-img\"/><div class=\"icons-sticky-el-text\"><h5>Applications For Runes and Ordinals</h5><p class=\"text-p-faded-2\">Easily build fungible and non-fungible token applications that are compatible with other protocols like Runes and Ordinals.</p></div></div><div class=\"icons-sticky-el\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/674cf6e365dc4707c62a9964_icons-sticky-icon-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"icons-sticky-el-img\"/><div class=\"icons-sticky-el-text\"><h5>DeFi</h5><p class=\"text-p-faded-2\">Thanks to these integrations with Runes and Ordinals, you can build exchanges, lending platforms, stablecoins and other DeFi applications.</p></div></div><div class=\"icons-sticky-el\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/674cf6e365dc4707c62a9960_icons-sticky-icon-4.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"icons-sticky-el-img\"/><div class=\"icons-sticky-el-text\"><h5>Enterprise Applications</h5><p class=\"text-p-faded-2\">Enable frictionless collaboration on shared data across multiple organizations. We can help keep data synchronized, obliviating costly and often manual reconciliation processes.<br/><br/>Plus, maintain easy access to all historical versions with timestamps and cryptographic signatures of all updates.<br/></p></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section-benefits-v1\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"benefits-v1-headline\"><div data-w-id=\"d3197296-ac14-ab0d-e270-c7370428a1ae\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name black\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">How to Get started</div></div><h3>Getting Started is Easy </h3><h6 class=\"heading-5\">We make building Web3 apps as easy as building Web2 apps.</h6></div><div class=\"benefits-v1-grid\"><div id=\"w-node-b606ff1a-a3af-0b7c-06fc-8c71565c9bbf-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-list\"><div class=\"benefits-v1-el\"><div id=\"w-node-b606ff1a-a3af-0b7c-06fc-8c71565c9bc1-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-el-number\"><h6>01</h6></div><div id=\"w-node-b606ff1a-a3af-0b7c-06fc-8c71565c9bc4-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-el-text\"><h6>Create an HTML file</h6><p class=\"benefits-v1-el-description\">Copy and paste the code from <a href=\"https://docs.bitcoincomputer.io/start/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p></div></div><div class=\"benefits-v1-el\"><div id=\"w-node-b606ff1a-a3af-0b7c-06fc-8c71565c9bca-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-el-number\"><h6>02</h6></div><div id=\"w-node-b606ff1a-a3af-0b7c-06fc-8c71565c9bcd-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-el-text\"><h6>Open it in your browser</h6><p class=\"benefits-v1-el-description\">Try to double click it or drag it in</p></div></div><div class=\"benefits-v1-el\"><div id=\"w-node-_5ceffdac-4a72-a294-267b-599c9f3ebe20-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-el-number\"><h6>03</h6></div><div id=\"w-node-_5ceffdac-4a72-a294-267b-599c9f3ebe23-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-el-text\"><h6>That&#x27;s all!</h6><p class=\"benefits-v1-el-description\">You executed a smart contract<br/>on our free testnet</p></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-b606ff1a-a3af-0b7c-06fc-8c71565c9bdb-c62a963d\" class=\"benefits-v1-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/678e96011a0b8ea6a6efe7e2_45449257d3e8c321faec51e200cdff10_photo_2025-01-20%2013.28.32.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-6\"/></div></div></div><section class=\"section-icons-sticky\"><div class=\"wrapper\"></div></section><div class=\"wrapper\"></div></section><section class=\"section-blocks\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"blocks-text\"><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7f2-c62a963d\" data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7f2\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"blocks-headline\"><h2>Example Applications</h2></div></div><div class=\"blocks-list\"><div class=\"blocks-el\"><div id=\"w-node-c94a3e8d-4eb3-40b7-b511-60127fc79fb2-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67a7468a6a95711ab2becfb0_Untitled%205.png\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" data-w-id=\"c94a3e8d-4eb3-40b7-b511-60127fc79fb3\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-img\"/></div><div id=\"w-node-c94a3e8d-4eb3-40b7-b511-60127fc79fb4-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-content\"><div data-w-id=\"c94a3e8d-4eb3-40b7-b511-60127fc79fb5\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name black\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">on-chain Order Book</div></div><h4 data-w-id=\"c94a3e8d-4eb3-40b7-b511-60127fc79fb8\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"blocks-content-headline\">A DEX on Bitcoin</h4><p data-w-id=\"c94a3e8d-4eb3-40b7-b511-60127fc79fba\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\">DEXs on Ethereum use automated market makers (AMMs), not because they are better trading algorithms, but because optimal trading algorithms require too much compute for Ethereum to handle. In fact, AMMs lead to slippage and inefficient trade execution.<br/>‍<br/>Order books, the best trading algorithms known to man, become available for DEXs for the first time through the Bitcoin Computer. If you would like to demo our order book based DEX, please <a href=\"mailto:clemens@bitcoincomputer.io?subject=Contact%3A%20DEX\">contact us.</a></p><a href=\"mailto:clemens@bitcoincomputer.io?subject=Demo%20Request%3A%20Dex\" class=\"button-2 w-button\">Request a demo</a></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el\"><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d802-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-content reversed\"><div data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d803\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name black\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">Chess For Money</div></div><h5 data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d806\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"blocks-content-headline\">Build Real Money Games</h5><p data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d808\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\">Real world games require too much compute for Ethereum. For example, determining if a position in chess is winning exceeds the compute available in an entire Ethereum block.<br/>‍<br/>We are building an open source chess implementation, where two players can put down some coins that the winner gets at the end of the game. <br/><br/></p><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin-computer/monorepo/tree/main/packages/chess-app\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button-2 w-button\">Github Repo</a></div><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d80a-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/67a1459ec73d13b0b2217f8e_photo_2025-02-03%2017.37.37.jpeg\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d80b\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-img\"/></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el\"><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d820-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/678e964de297a640135e0307_photo_2025-01-20%2013.28.35.jpeg\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d821\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-img\"/></div><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d818-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-content reversed\"><div data-w-id