 w-button\">Trade NFTs</a></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el\"><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7f9-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-content\"><div data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7fa\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name black\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">Block Explorer</div></div><h5 data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7fd\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"blocks-content-headline\">Create and update on-chain assets with ease</h5><p data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7ff\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\">With our blockchain explorer, you can browse, create, and update on-chain assets. <br/><br/>You can build smart objects on Bitcoin, and update assets you own by calling any function. </p><a href=\"https://explorer.bitcoincomputer.io/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button-2 w-button\">Explore Bitcoin</a></div><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7f7-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/678e962a28b585a88f88e384_photo_2025-01-20%2013.28.38.jpeg\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"716\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" alt=\"Bitcoin Computer Explorer\" data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d7f8\" class=\"blocks-img\"/></div></div><div class=\"blocks-el\"><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d80d-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-img-container\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/678e963ec6673f8713b23051_photo_2025-01-20%2013.28.36.jpeg\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d80e\" alt=\"\" class=\"blocks-img\"/></div><div id=\"w-node-e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d80f-c62a963d\" class=\"blocks-content\"><div data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d810\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"section-name black\"><div class=\"section-name-text\">Non-Custodial Wallet</div></div><h4 data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d813\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\" class=\"blocks-content-headline\">An Open Source Solution For On-Chain Assets</h4><p data-w-id=\"e6033950-0d69-8ee9-588d-914aa630d815\" style=\"-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 50px, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0\">Try our open-source non-custodial wallet that can store both your money and on-chain assets across Bitcoin, Litecoin, Dogecoin, Bitcoin Cash and Pepecoin.<br/>  <br/>If you&#x27;re a wallet developer that wants to integrate support for on-chain assets on Bitcoin into your product have a look at the <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin-computer/monorepo/tree/main/packages/wallet#readme\">Github repo</a>.</p><a href=\"https://wallet.bitcoincomputer.io/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button-2 w-button\">Demo the wallet</a></div></div></div></div><div data-hover=\"false\" data-delay=\"0\" data-w-id=\"1d5a4935-1d6a-968e-9585-3fd945f88ef7\" class=\"qna-dropdown w-dropdown\"><div class=\"qna-dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle\"><h5 class=\"qna2-heading\">Need Development Support?</h5><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/68b882a386de1ccf4bd2d31c_Metarune%20Labs%20Text%20-%20Black.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 92vw, (max-width: 991px) 94vw, (max-width: 1537px) 96vw, 1476px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/68b882a386de1ccf4bd2d31c_Metarune%20Labs%20Text%20-%20Black-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/68b882a386de1ccf4bd2d31c_Metarune%20Labs%20Text%20-%20Black-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/68b882a386de1ccf4bd2d31c_Metarune%20Labs%20Text%20-%20Black-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/674cf6e265dc4707c62a960b/68b882a386de1ccf4bd2d31c_Metarune%20Labs%20Text%20-%20Black.jpg 1476w\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-7\"/></div><nav class=\"qna-dropdown-list w-dropdown-list\"><div>MetaRune Labs is our official development partner. They are highly experienced in Web 3 development and have build several applications on the Bitcoin Computer. If you need help in making your idea a reality, please contact clemens@bitcoincomputer.io and we will get you in touch.<br/></div></nav></div><section data-w-id=\"892e70bb-92ab-cf98-e8a8-b4da7f0792de\" class=\"section-cta\"><div class=\"wrapper\"><div class=\"cta-container\"><div class=\"cta-text\"><h2 data-w-id=\"892e70bb-92ab-cf98-e8a8-b4da7f0792e2\" class=\"cta-headline\">Build Your First Javascript Smart Contract In Your Browser</h2><div data-w-id=\"892e70bb-92ab-cf98-e8a8-b4da7f0792e4\" class=\"cta-button\"><div class=\"button-border-container\"><a href=\"https://explorer.bitcoincomputer.io/playground\" class=\"button button-border dark-bg w-inline-block\"><div class=\"button-flex-container\"><div class=\"button-text\">Try Our Playground</div></div></a></div><a href=\"https://docs.bitcoincomputer.io/\" class=\"button button-ligh